questions.stem:
A provider creates the following share:

CREATE SHARE financial_data_share;
GRANT USAGE ON DATABASE finance_db TO SHARE financial_data_share;
GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA finance_db.public TO SHARE financial_data_share;
GRANT SELECT ON TABLE finance_db.public.transactions TO SHARE financial_data_share;

A consumer mounts this share and queries it heavily. Which account pays for the compute credits consumed by the consumer's queries?
